{"tid":706660,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"強烈譴責會員「蝦仔爹哋」借本人上位，令人髮指！","createTime":"2018-06-18T05:30:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-18T16:11:52.000Z","uid":82917,"like":15,"dislike":35,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"03513fc38da0c16cf3640dbce13548c3420a9bb9","tid":706660,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T05:30:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/705560/page/2?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/705560/page/2?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">精彩留言節錄</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/18/132715_009d0fd268fb2de3ee8b4950127d3206.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F18%2F132715_009d0fd268fb2de3ee8b4950127d3206.png&h=a5974dbe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/18/132716_c51928ca2f5cf2d18c021177689400f5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F18%2F132716_c51928ca2f5cf2d18c021177689400f5.png&h=1966d2dd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/18/132719_f7468b81fe402319767ab8fae392629a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F18%2F132719_f7468b81fe402319767ab8fae392629a.png&h=9d054bf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n哎呀！睇返真係好鬼死柒架姐。<br />\n第一頁最衰真係我件分身蛋散啦，<br />\n覆得咁鬼肉酸，簡直拆我生招牌！<br />\n我哋呢啲打手account廿四小時都有人上架嘛。<br />\n條友真係唔識架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得個幾隻爛鬼正皮就廿文廿武，<br />\n話你唔係捕住我都冇人信啦！<br />\n今日駁唔到人就「識你老鼠」、「00後中學TB」，<br />\n成隻小學雞咁含沙射影，勁鬼肉酸！<br />\n連登唔岩你上呀，扯吧啦。<br />\n<br />\n我係邊個關你撚事咩，借我上位真是可恥！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a46077a910a3acad7ca531fd76bf0428d1d94d